# Xcode (the App/ project) — derived data, user state, build output.
# GedReader.xcodeproj is GENERATED by XcodeGen from App/project.yml (the source of truth),
# so it's not committed — run `xcodegen generate` in App/ to recreate it.
App/GedReader.xcodeproj/
build/
DerivedData/
*.xcodeproj/xcuserdata/
*.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate

